HEADWORD: Modiste
<hw>Mo`diste"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>Mode</er>; cf. <er>Modist</er>.]</ety> <def>One, esp. a woman, who
makes, or deals in, articles of fashion, esp. of the fashionable dress
